---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const phone = '01623 325 123';
const telHref = `tel:${phone.replace(/\s+/g, '')}`;
const town = 'Newark';
---

<BaseLayout
  title={`Mobile Tyre Fitting in ${town} | 24/7 A1 & A46 Tyre Service`}
  description={`24/7 mobile tyre fitting and emergency callouts in ${town}-on-Trent and along the A1 corridor. 20-minute average ETA from Bilsthorpe. Call 01623 325 123.`}
>
  <section class="area-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="eyebrow">{town}</span>
      <h1>Mobile Tyre Fitting in {town}</h1>
      <p class="area-intro">
        Newark is one of Dean&rsquo;s closest postcodes &mdash; Bilsthorpe is ten minutes up the road and the average ETA into central Newark is 20 minutes. He covers Newark itself and the surrounding villages from Collingham to Coddington and Farndon, as well as the A1 and A46 corridors. Roadside, driveway, business park, car park &mdash; wherever the car is, that&rsquo;s where the job gets done.
      </p>
      <div class="cta-row">
        <a class="btn btn-primary btn-call" href={telHref}>
          <span aria-hidden="true">&#9742;</span> Call: {phone}
        </a>
        <a class="btn btn-outline" href="/#quote">Get a Quote</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-white">
    <div class="container container-narrow">
      <span class="eyebrow" style="color: var(--color-accent);">Why Choose Us in {town}</span>
      <h2>Three reasons {town} drivers call us first</h2>
      <ul class="area-points">
        <li class="area-point">
          <h3>The closest unit to {town}</h3>
          <p>Our Bilsthorpe base is the nearest properly equipped mobile fitter to Newark. That isn&rsquo;t marketing &mdash; it&rsquo;s a postcode fact, and you&rsquo;ll feel it in the ETA.</p>
        </li>
        <li class="area-point">
          <h3>Fast A1 response</h3>
          <p>The A1 through Newark produces a steady flow of tyre emergencies. Dean is REACT licensed and experienced in working safely on fast A-roads when a car has had a blowout at speed.</p>
        </li>
        <li class="area-point">
          <h3>Trusted by Newark businesses</h3>
          <p>Several local trade businesses and fleet operators use Dean as their first call. Same-day response, fixed pricing, and no hassle.</p>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-darker">
    <div class="container container-narrow">
      <span class="eyebrow">Nearby Areas Also Covered</span>
      <h2>Same fast service across the {town} catchment</h2>
      <p class="text-muted">If you&rsquo;re heading north or south on the A1, or out towards Lincoln on the A46, we&rsquo;ve got the area covered. Click any nearby town for more:</p>
      <div class="tag-cloud">
        <a class="tag" href="/areas/southwell/">Southwell</a>
        <a class="tag" href="/areas/lincoln/">Lincoln</a>
        <a class="tag" href="/areas/grantham/">Grantham</a>
        <a class="tag" href="/areas/mansfield/">Mansfield</a>
        <a class="tag" href="/areas/tuxford/">Tuxford</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-light service-cta-section">
    <div class="container container-narrow text-center">
      <h2>Stuck in {town}?</h2>
      <p class="text-muted-dark">Dean is properly local. Call the number and you&rsquo;ll have a real ETA and a fixed price within minutes.</p>
      <a class="btn btn-primary btn-call" href={telHref}>
        <span aria-hidden="true">&#9742;</span> Call {phone}
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
